{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-js","path":"/2012/08/22/安裝有支援Silverlight、WPF、StechFlow版本的Blend-for-Visual-Studio/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"安裝有支援Silverlight、WPF、StechFlow版本的Blend for Visual Studio","date":"22 August 2012","author":"Sky Chang","excerpt":null,"tags":["Silveright","Tools","Visual Studio","WPF"],"coverImage":null},"id":"22a54c89-82f1-5107-858a-d262ad8d5ba5","html":"<p>為什麼要下這個標題!?裝完Visual Studio 2012後，不就會有Blend for Visual Studio了嗎??理由很簡單，大家看下圖就知道了，使用Blend for Visual Studio是不支援Silverlight、WPF的!! ( 他只能開Win 8 APP… )</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://lh4.ggpht.com/-IHpUnxb6hhM/UDRIq1b4yWI/AAAAAAAAENo/ZojuhKol5sI/s1600-h/image%25255B24%25255D.png\"><img src=\"http://lh3.ggpht.com/-07jZwgHUuL8/UDRIryMzChI/AAAAAAAAENs/Dmitz49bG1E/image_thumb%25255B8%25255D.png?imgmax=800\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"></a></p>\n<p>目前<a href=\"http://blendinsider.com/technical/announcing-blend-sketchflow-preview-for-visual-studio-2012-2012-08-15/\">官方</a>也指出，他們也很抱歉，並且在努力改進…，而目前也提供了一個Blend + StechFlow Preview版本來解決Silverlight和WPF的問題；但同樣的，官方也提到一些授權問題，並且也提供了對應表，讓大家知道哪個版本可以開甚麼專案… ( 真的不想在這邊抱怨…)</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://lh3.ggpht.com/-GpdKGhiNe6s/UDRIsjv0h9I/AAAAAAAAEN4/ZXta7KHkcUk/s1600-h/image%25255B30%25255D.png\"><img src=\"http://lh3.ggpht.com/-i4EXp_9VBnE/UDRIt0GbcEI/AAAAAAAAEN8/K__dctMbqQ8/image_thumb%25255B11%25255D.png?imgmax=800\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"></a></p>\n<p>好吧，回到重點，我們可以從這邊進行<a href=\"http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/confirmation.aspx?id=30702\">下載</a>，然後開始安裝。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://lh3.ggpht.com/-hKEAwZYt-48/UDRIvOHuovI/AAAAAAAAEOI/7Ur1-GNtLtE/s1600-h/image%25255B31%25255D.png\"><img src=\"http://lh5.ggpht.com/-IfOj8B2sVbU/UDRIwMM0ptI/AAAAAAAAEOM/jV1wW_TFW68/image_thumb%25255B12%25255D.png?imgmax=800\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"></a></p>\n<p>安裝過程。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://lh4.ggpht.com/-gNEqHoPLM58/UDRIw9CMmsI/AAAAAAAAEOU/vAU-jReRlFk/s1600-h/image%25255B32%25255D.png\"><img src=\"http://lh4.ggpht.com/-rcVorLesDcs/UDRIx15cusI/AAAAAAAAEOc/qRSmxVFVY9c/image_thumb%25255B13%25255D.png?imgmax=800\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"></a></p>\n<p>到這邊就安裝好了。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://lh6.ggpht.com/-08-6MFZCXRA/UDRIy6eep7I/AAAAAAAAEOo/-G2ptvsJ6nw/s1600-h/image%25255B33%25255D.png\"><img src=\"http://lh6.ggpht.com/-NXAiW23xAlg/UDRIz-8qd8I/AAAAAAAAEOs/b8hmrBsjHdE/image_thumb%25255B14%25255D.png?imgmax=800\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"></a></p>\n<p>然後我們可以從開始列裡面發現多了一個Blend + StechFlow Preview。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://lh6.ggpht.com/-fBjhYILPTWE/UDRI0rzPhaI/AAAAAAAAEO4/TmUhWwSdR-8/s1600-h/image%25255B25%25255D.png\"><img src=\"http://lh6.ggpht.com/-fzqeKqymS6k/UDRI1yZS-9I/AAAAAAAAEO8/uDDme95Zgmc/image_thumb%25255B9%25255D.png?imgmax=800\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"></a></p>\n<p>開啟畫面，就很明顯地寫著Preview。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://lh3.ggpht.com/--3yjwtnKyMU/UDRI3D1-wfI/AAAAAAAAEPE/wv8Pjn5gBLM/s1600-h/image%25255B34%25255D.png\"><img src=\"http://lh4.ggpht.com/-q2mT_ytpmBw/UDRI4IRnWLI/AAAAAAAAEPQ/vu8CRNXUyYU/image_thumb%25255B15%25255D.png?imgmax=800\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"></a></p>\n<p>打開後，就可以讀取Silverlight的XMAL了…</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://lh5.ggpht.com/-frMzVIWeYL4/UDRI5Ojw03I/AAAAAAAAEPY/TD1y6YcvJ-0/s1600-h/image%25255B35%25255D.png\"><img src=\"http://lh4.ggpht.com/-FWQhyKrupEg/UDRI6HM_JsI/AAAAAAAAEPg/1QXqkNoRReU/image_thumb%25255B16%25255D.png?imgmax=800\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"></a></p>\n<p>就這樣…</p>\n<h4>後記</h4>\n<p>只能說，這個過渡時期，如果有需要的人，就在等等，或是直接衝了…</p>\n<h4>參考網址</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://blendinsider.com/technical/announcing-blend-sketchflow-preview-for-visual-studio-2012-2012-08-15/\" title=\"http://blendinsider.com/technical/announcing-blend-sketchflow-preview-for-visual-studio-2012-2012-08-15/\">http://blendinsider.com/technical/announcing-blend-sketchflow-preview-for-visual-studio-2012-2012-08-15/</a></li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"為什麼要下這個標題!?裝完Visual Studio 2012後，不就會有Blend for Visual Studio了嗎??理由很簡單，大家看下圖就知道了，使用Blend for Visual Studio是不支援Silverlight、WPF的!! ( 他只能開Win…"}},"pageContext":{"type":"posts","next":{"frontmatter":{"path":null,"title":"Visual Studio - 使用.NET Framework原始碼來偵錯","tags":["C#","Visual Studio"]},"fields":{"slug":"/2012/08/21/Visual-Studio-使用-NET-Framework原始碼來偵錯/"},"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/runner/work/blog.sanc.idv.tw/blog.sanc.idv.tw/src/posts/blog.sanc.idv.tw/Visual-Studio-使用-NET-Framework原始碼來偵錯.md"},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"path":null,"title":"","tags":["Azure"]},"fields":{"slug":"/2012/08/23/Windows-Azure-注意-超過免費額度的話-東西會被自動移除/"},"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/runner/work/blog.sanc.idv.tw/blog.sanc.idv.tw/src/posts/blog.sanc.idv.tw/Windows-Azure-注意-超過免費額度的話-東西會被自動移除.md"}}}}